content: CFS-T S Cable modules (STRF) Modules to seal cables within transit frames which penetrate switch cabinets ### Categories: Home > Products > Firestop & fire protection > Cable transit frames and penetration sealing systems- - - ### FEATURES:Features Simplified inventory management – only 4 different modules are needed to cover all cable diameters from 3 to 33 mm Time-saving installation thanks to module interlinking, especially where cables run vertically through switch cabinets Color-coded adapter system to make inspection easier and more reliable Applications Sealing cables within transit frames which penetrate switch cabinets For approval or certificate information, please see individual items. ### TECHNICAL DATA: Temperature resistance range: -40 - 122 °F Free from: Halogen (halogen content <= 0.1 weight %) Reaction to fire class (EN 13501-1): E Technical Data | Temperature resistance range | -40 - 122 °F | Free from | Halogen (halogen content <= 0.1 weight %) | Reaction to fire class (EN 13501-1) | E ### ITEMS- 2042718 - Cable module CFS-T S 15/0+3-9 - Package Size 128 pc - 2042719 - Cable module CFS-T S 20/0+5-12 - Package Size 72 pc - 2042720 - Cable module CFS-T S 30/0+13-23 - Package Size 32 pc - 2042721 - Cable module CFS-T S 40/0+23-33 - Package Size 18 pc - 2042722 - Filler module CFS-T FB S 24x5/0 - Package Size 72 pc - 2042723 - Filler module CFS-T FB S 12x10/0 - Package Size 36 pc
